//TestCase Summary: 										Verify that existing user is able to add a credit card to account.
//What the script does/TestCase Description:				Following is what Scripts does
//															1. Calls the Reusable action signin with the username and password in TestData.ini file
//															2. Navigates to Accounts page of the account.
//															3. Calls the reusable action to add card to the account.
//															2. After the reusable action it make sure that card got added to the account.
